.\}
.nf
Da XQueryDeviceState request queries tha state of a input
device\&. Da current state of keys n' buttons (up or down), and
valuators (current value) on tha thang is reported by this
request\&. Each key or button is represented by a lil' bit up in the
XDeviceState structure dat is returned\&. Valuators on the
device report 0 if they is reportin relatizzle shiznit, and
the current value if they is reportin absolute shiznit\&.
.fi
